Bacchae are crazed Petitioners native to Arborea, blessed by the gods Dionysus or Pan. They wander the Plane, drinking wine and celebrating, often abducting those who they encounter to make them part of their endless revels. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Planes of Chaos        
              
                    Fiend Folio (D&amp;D 3.4)